summary: The Elder Maul is a powerful and unique item in OldSchool RuneScape
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds the Elder Maul to Skyrim, It has the same stats as a Daedric WarHammer and the same items/requirements to make one minus a daedra heart. You need 6 ebony ingots and 3 leather strips along with Daedric Smithing perk.


If you have any feed back post here or message me on RuneScape : UFOs
author: UFOs
